California Confidentiality of Medical Information Act ("CMIA")
Evolution Nutrition is committed to ensuring, through the implementation of prudent and reasonable controls, that the individually identifiable medical information it receives from its consumers ("Medical Information") is safeguarded. As a general rule, Evolution Nutrition will not disclose Medical Information without first obtaining a written authorization from the respective consumer, unless such disclosure is permitted or required by applicable law. For example, Evolution Nutrition is required to disclose Medical Information if it is compelled to do so under court order or search warrant. Evolution Nutrition may also disclose Medical Information, without a consumer's written authorization, to health care professionals involved in the consumer's care, to a family member involved with the consumer's care or payment related to the consumer's care, to an entity assisting Evolution Nutrition with its administrative services, to governmental oversight agencies, to a third party for purposes of anonymizing or encrypting the data, and in certain other specified circumstances permitted or required under applicable state and federal law.
Children's Privacy
Evolution Nutrition is very sensitive to the issue of children's privacy. Our Site and Evolution Nutrition's products and services are neither developed for, nor directed at, children under the age of 13. If you believe your child under the age of 13 has provided Evolution Nutrition with personally identifiable information, or created an account at our Site, and you would like to have the information removed, please contact us at at
info@evolutionnutrition.com
or Evolution Nutrition, Inc., attn.: Marketing 228 S. Cedros, Suite E, Solana Beach, CA 92075
Children under the age of 18 but at least 13 years of age may use our Site only under the supervision of a parent or legal guardian. If you believe your child under the age of 18 but at least 13 years of age has provided Evolution Nutrition with personally identifiable information, or created an account at our Site, without your supervision and you would like to have the information removed, please contact us at at
info@evolutionnutrition.com
or Evolution Nutrition, Inc., attn.: Marketing 228 S. Cedros, Suite E, Solana Beach, CA 92075
International User Notice
For international users, please note that it may be necessary to transfer your information internationally and, in particular, your information may be transferred to and processed in the United States.
For residents of the European Union: the data protection and other laws of other countries outside of the European Union may not be as comprehensive as those of the European Union. Please be assured that we take steps to ensure that your privacy is protected as described in this Privacy Policy. By using our Site, you agree to have your information used and transferred to the United States as set forth in this policy.
Security
Evolution Nutrition uses commercially reasonable physical, managerial and technical safeguards to preserve the integrity and security of your personal information. We cannot, however, ensure or warrant the security of any information you transmit to Evolution Nutrition and you transmit such information at your own risk. Once we receive your transmission of information, Evolution Nutrition makes commercially reasonable efforts to ensure the security of our systems. However, please note that this is not a guarantee that such information may not be accessed, disclosed, altered or destroyed by breach of any of our physical, managerial or technical safeguards.
Changes to Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy is subject to change without notice. We may change this Privacy Policy at any time, with immediate effect, by posting a new version of it on our Site. If, however, we intend to disclose or otherwise use users' personally identifiable information in a manner different from that stated in this Privacy Policy at the time of collection, we will post a notice of such intent on our Site 30 days prior to such action.
